    {
      "postText": "\u201cFrom cold calls in clinic lobbies to powering a million patient conversations \u2014 Confido Health is redefining the sound of healthcare.\u201d\n\nWhen we met Chetan Reddy and Vichar Shroff, they were two relentless founders in New York, living inside clinics, shadowing front-desk staff, iterating endlessly to find real Product-Market Fit.\nIn just a year since we led their Seed (Sep \u201924) \u2014 they\u2019ve grown 20\u00d7, powering access for 1M+ patients across hundreds of sites where hold times have dropped to zero.\n\nToday, as we double down in their Series A, Confido has become the platform of choice for multi-location chains across specialties.\n\nAfter nailing scheduling with 95% call success rates, they\u2019re now automating payment collections, prescription refills, closing care gaps \u2014 the critical front-door workflows of healthcare.\nProud to have been their first believers, and even prouder to back them again as they scale this category-defining healthcare AI company \n\nOnwards & upwards @Confido Health \ud83d\udcaa\nTogether with Blume Ventures Sanjay Nath Aakash Kumar DeVC Shivam Rajvanshi Manav Garg Girish Mathrubootham Lakshmi Shankar",
      "image": null,
      "postLink": "https://www.linkedin.com/feed/update/urn:li:activity:7382014988334526464?updateEntityUrn=urn%3Ali%3Afs_feedUpdate%3A%28V2%2Curn%3Ali%3Aactivity%3A7382014988334526464%29",
      "subTitle": null,
      "title": null,
      "type": "Post"
    },
    {
      "postText": "It\u2019s just been 2 years since we launched Together but it feels like a lifetime. \n\nThese have been incredible 2 years of our lives - full of love from founders and the startup ecosystem, incredible learnings from our portfolio companies and the journey of a lifetime with my partners Manav, Girish Mathrubootham and our team Shivam, Pratyush \u2601\ufe0f & Kaushik. \n\nContinuing our mission to back iconic companies, we are happy to announce the launch of our $150M Fund II to back SaaS and AI founders.\n\nRishen, Ruchin, Rohit, Brijraj , Achuthanand, Sudharshan, Vishalini, Vaibhav, Prashant, Sol, Sudheer, Krishna, Siddharth, Rajiv, Gautam, Shuveb, Vishal, Bala, Abhishek, Aravind, Soham, Meet, Karan, Akshat, Amar, Arjun, Ethan,  Dushyant, Jot, Abhinay\n\nThanks to all of you for making this happen. Looking forward to having more fun in this journey with Fund II and beyond. Together Forever!\n\nhttps://lnkd.in/g3B7fyBq\n\n#saas #genai #indianstartups #startup",
      "image": null,
      "postLink": "https://www.linkedin.com/feed/update/urn:li:activity:7090233588041846784?updateEntityUrn=urn%3Ali%3Afs_feedUpdate%3A%28V2%2Curn%3Ali%3Aactivity%3A7090233588041846784%29",
